name: Pset_DistributionPortTypeAudioVisual
definition: Audio-visual port occurrence attributes attached to an instance of IfcDistributionPort.

properties.name: ConnectionType
properties.definition: The physical port connection:DIN: DIN connector.DSub: D-Subminature connector.DVI: Digital Video Interface.EIAJ: fiberoptic digital audio.HDMI: High-Definition Multimedia Interface.RCA: analog audio or video.TRS: analog audio jack plug.XLR: XLR connector.

localizations.name: 接続タイプ
localizations.definition: 物理ポート接続：- DIN: DIN コネクタ- DSub: D-Subコネクタ- DVI: デジタルビデオ端子- EIAJ: 光ファイバーデジタルオーディオ- HDMI: HDMI端子- RCA: アナログオーディオ或いはビデオ- TRS: アナログオーディオジャックプラグ.- XLR: XLR コネクタ

localizations.name: 연결 유형
localizations.definition: DIN : DIN 커넥터 DSub : D-Sub 커넥터 DVI : 디지털 비디오 단자 EIAJ : 광섬유 디지털 오디오 HDMI : HDMI 단자 RCA : 아날로그 오디오 또는 비디오 TRS : 아날로그 오디오 잭 플러그. XLR : XLR 커넥터

properties.name: ConnectionSubtype
properties.definition: The physical port connection subtype that further qualifies the ConnectionType.  The following values are recommended:DIN: Mini3P, Mini4P, Mini5P, Mini6P, Mini7P, Mini8P, Mini9P DSub: DA15, DB25, DC37, DD50, DE9, DE15 EIAJ: RC5720HDMI: A, B, CTRS: TS_Mini, TS_SubMini, TRS_Mini, TRS_SubMini

localizations.name: 接続サブタイプ
localizations.definition: 物理ポート接続のサブタイプ。接続タイプ以外の情報を設定する場合に使用。下記の値を設定：- DIN: Mini3P, Mini4P, Mini5P, Mini6P, Mini7P, Mini8P, Mini9P - DSub: DA15, DB25, DC37, DD50, DE9, DE15 - EIAJ: RC5720- HDMI: A, B, C- TRS: TS_Mini, TS_SubMini, - TRS_Mini, TRS_SubMinii

localizations.name: 연결 서브 타입
localizations.definition: DIN : Mini3P, Mini4P, Mini5P, Mini6P, Mini7P, Mini8P, Mini9P DSub : DA15, DB25, DC37, DD50, DE9, DE15 EIAJ : RC5720 HDMI : A, B, C TRS : TS_Mini, TS_SubMini, TRS_Mini, TRS_SubMini

localizations.name: 接続ジェンダー
localizations.definition: 形状的な接続ジェンダー（オス、メス、その他、未知、未設定）。

properties.name: AudioChannel
properties.definition: Indicates the audio channel or NONE if no audio.

localizations.name: オーディオチャネル
localizations.definition: オーディオチャネルを示す値。オーディオがない場合NONEを設定。

properties.name: VideoChannel
properties.definition: Indicates the video channel or NONE if no video.

localizations.name: ビデオチャネル
localizations.definition: ビデオチャネルを示す値。ビデオがない場合NONEを設定。
